FBIS4-35759 "drnes107_n_94004" FBIS-NES-94-107 Daily Report 2 Jun 1994 LEBANON Israeli Overflights, Shelling Continue in South Israeli Overflights, Shelling Continue in South Planes Drop Flares, Thermal Balloons NC0206195294 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 1914 GMT 2 Jun 94 NC0206195294 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] We received this report a short time ago. Israeli warplanes have been flying at a low altitude over south Lebanon since 2130 this evening, particularly over al-Nabatiyah and Iqlim al-Tuffah. The planes have been dropping thermal balloons and flares over the central sector of the south.
